# Security and secrets

- Never commit: `.env`, `.env.local`, `*.pem`, `*.key`, credentials JSON, real API keys.
- EC2 deploy: only GitHub Secrets (`EC2_HOST`, `EC2_USER`, `EC2_SSH_KEY`). No PEM in repo or public docs.
- Do not paste private keys or live credentials into issues, README, or chat exports in `docs/decisions/`.
- Use `.env.example` for placeholder names only.

See [docs/SECURITY.md](docs/SECURITY.md).
